{"tid":2379241,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"熱門韓劇《驅魔麵館》結局收視率大幅回升，官宣確定製作第二季！","createTime":"2021-01-25T05:56:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-30T14:51:56.000Z","uid":16659,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"df0c0fc2b71b793ca2b4e2d249beb23bac5d92df","tid":2379241,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T05:56:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_54d1f681df55dd04d9154c69bf7ba57f/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-01-25/133256-894717.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_54d1f681df55dd04d9154c69bf7ba57f%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-01-25%2F133256-894717.jpg&h=7c5df681&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n網友：「一定要是原班人馬啊！！！」<br />\n<br />\nOCN 熱門韓劇《驅魔麵館》（驚奇的傳聞）終於在昨晚迎來第16集大結局，除了收視率大幅回升完美收官，官方更正式宣布確定會製作第二季。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_fc6fdb8b4ce23a823384e4d8ed266966/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-01-25/133256-894718.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_fc6fdb8b4ce23a823384e4d8ed266966%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-01-25%2F133256-894718.jpg&h=7f10de9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《驅魔麵館》從第一集AGB全國收視率2.702%，一路飆升至第12集10.581%，最後一集在有線台、IPTV、衛星綜合的收費平台收視率中，以平均11%、最高11.9%，刷新了自身最高收視率，創下了OCN歷代最高收視率，寫下全新歷史。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_887c95ac0af7a9b54003894864df685f/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-01-25/133256-894719.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_887c95ac0af7a9b54003894864df685f%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-01-25%2F133256-894719.jpg&h=d1495d63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而就在今天早上，相關人士透露：「官方確定會製作第二季，但拍攝日程和編製時間等具體事項都還沒有確定，主演劉俊相、趙炳圭、金世正、廉惠蘭是否加入也正在協調中。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_90d6441bf745bf1a6aa20c9f2f0758de/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-01-25/133256-894720.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_90d6441bf745bf1a6aa20c9f2f0758de%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-01-25%2F133256-894720.jpg&h=1aaf5d53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n追完《驅魔麵館》後，大家是否期待第二季的到來呢？"},{"pid":"9c659f081fb9b0f8e7ba77dd245e9d352c92e1df","tid":2379241,"uid":229026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T05:57:35.000Z","msg":"好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20e3d014ad7c29c61c1efd8103124f2f10c6345b","tid":2379241,"uid":256952,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T06:01:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n8PitJt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn8PitJt.png&h=b9f9998d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"edd72df86f885017a3102f679bc7d497e71e5ec3","tid":2379241,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"20e3d014ad7c29c61c1efd8103124f2f10c6345b","tid":2379241,"uid":256952,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T06:01:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n8PitJt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn8PitJt.png&h=b9f9998d&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T06:02:33.000Z","msg":"what the hell!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edd893297df368479a8258e0527306f055fc7162","tid":2379241,"uid":261849,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T06:04:01.000Z","msg":"岩岩睇緊大結局<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a1725706cba44b3528aa551e54ebf6239a39ab3","tid":2379241,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"edd72df86f